		<div id="text-176994025" class="p">
			
		 	
				Meta is partnering with Blumhouse to launch "Movie Mate" technology that encourages moviegoers to <a href="https://variety.com/2025/film/news/meta-second-screen-theater-tech-m3gan-rerelease-1236364712/">use their phones during theatrical screenings</a>, beginning with an April 30 showing of "Megan" at Blumhouse's "Halfway to Halloween Film Festival." According to Variety, the system enables viewers to chat with a Megan-themed AI chatbot, answer trivia questions, and access behind-the-scenes information while watching the film in theaters.
		 	
